00:23:08.870 --> 00:23:09.995
zeyer gut.

00:23:10.271 --> 00:23:11.970
zeyer gut gedenk ikh.

00:23:12.110 --> 00:23:17.572
az me hot zikh nit gegloybt vos do, vos do tut zikh. glaykh dem ershtn tog zaynen bay undz shoyn geven

00:23:17.662 --> 00:23:20.756
a- antlofene fun Tavrik, vayle Tavrik

00:23:20.756 --> 00:23:22.888
iz oyfn grenets mit Daytshland.

00:23:23.383 --> 00:23:25.166
iz glaykh, dos iz geven

00:23:25.661 --> 00:23:29.818
zeks a zeyger in der fri, hobn mir shoyn gevust az se iz der krig ongefangen.

00:23:29.818 --> 00:23:33.907
un di rusisher shoyn zaynen, gedenk ikh zaynen gelegn oyf der erd.

00:23:34.132 --> 00:23:35.268
hob ikh nokh gezogt,

00:23:35.268 --> 00:23:38.092
⟨oybe⟩ zey lign oyf der erd, lign mir in der erd.

00:23:38.452 --> 00:23:39.613
un azoy iz geven.

00:23:39.633 --> 00:23:43.452
un azoy vi, vi mir hobn gevust, ikh hob gevust az

00:23:43.452 --> 00:23:46.023
der ⟨yokobayetist⟩, der ⟨Mitshele⟩

00:23:46.586 --> 00:23:47.644
fun undz

00:23:48.037 --> 00:23:50.546
iz geven zeyer a groyser bandit,

00:23:50.670 --> 00:23:53.989
un er flegt ale mol fun undz lakhn,

00:23:54.062 --> 00:23:56.624
un er flegt zogn, az se vet nokh kumen a tsayt

00:23:56.624 --> 00:23:58.506
az ikh vel nemen fun aykh nekomen,

00:23:58.506 --> 00:24:03.624
un er flegt nemen mit di hent un vayzn azoy, azoy vel ikh aykh alemen oysshisn.

00:24:03.984 --> 00:24:06.088
zog ikh, mame lomir antloyfn.

00:24:06.161 --> 00:24:08.602
mir hobn, mir hobn gemeynt az

00:24:09.080 --> 00:24:12.056
azoy vi der shtroys vos bahalt der kop in zamd,

00:24:12.067 --> 00:24:15.962
un un er zet keynem nit, et- zet im oykh keyner nit.

00:24:15.962 --> 00:24:19.166
ober azoy iz nit geven, me hot undz umetum gefunen.

00:24:20.117 --> 00:24:21.883
umetum hot men undz gefunen.

00:24:24.150 --> 00:24:25.404
un

00:24:25.415 --> 00:24:28.129
yetst vil ikh dertseyln vi dos iz forgekumen

00:24:28.132 --> 00:24:30.270
az mir hobn gevandlt fun Kelm

00:24:30.528 --> 00:24:32.930
in Bilish⟨UNK⟩,

00:24:32.975 --> 00:24:35.011
in dorf Bilishk⟨UNK⟩,

00:24:35.102 --> 00:24:38.185
bay eynem YANKAUSKES.

00:24:39.978 --> 00:24:41.739
dos iz geven di gantse mishpokhe?

00:24:41.739 --> 00:24:42.453
yo.

00:24:42.662 --> 00:24:43.939
dray mentshn.

00:24:44.028 --> 00:24:47.380
in viflte tog fun mil- milkhome hot ir dos geton?

00:24:49.462 --> 00:24:50.941
ir ye.

00:24:49.850 --> 00:24:51.954
velkhe tog? g- glaykh dem ershtn tog.

00:24:51.825 --> 00:24:53.355
zayt ir aroysgegangen fun Kelm?

00:24:52.668 --> 00:24:53.425
yo.

00:24:53.425 --> 00:24:58.319
un gelozn nit farshlosn afile di tir. me flegt oykh nit farshlisn di tir un se dokh geven alts

00:24:58.319 --> 00:24:59.464
erlekh.

00:25:00.262 --> 00:25:04.492
nu, zaynen mir antlofn dortn in Bilishku,

00:25:05.088 --> 00:25:06.044
in dorf,

00:25:06.607 --> 00:25:10.106
bay dem YANKAUSKES, dortn a sakh yidishe gekumen.

00:25:10.106 --> 00:25:11.377
a sakh yidishe.

00:25:11.467 --> 00:25:12.604
in a,

00:25:12.615 --> 00:25:14.820
nit a shtal, nor azoy vi a,

00:25:15.028 --> 00:25:16.423
vi a kleyt.

00:25:16.580 --> 00:25:21.952
vu er, vu er flegt haltn di tvue in eyn zayt, un di tsveyte zayt mir geven oyf

00:25:21.952 --> 00:25:25.181
mit di peklekh, vifl a mentsh hot gekent mitnemen mit zikh.

00:25:25.592 --> 00:25:27.530
un nakher hobn mir gezen az

00:25:27.549 --> 00:25:32.032
me flegt bombardirn un altsding, hobn mir batrakht az me darf geyn vayter,

00:25:32.190 --> 00:25:35.273
zaynen mir gegangen a, nokh VAYBURA.

00:25:35.565 --> 00:25:38.023
dortn hobn mir, altsding tsu fus.

00:25:39.193 --> 00:25:43.052
dortn hobn mir ibergenekhtikt bay di familye Niselevitsh.

00:25:43.378 --> 00:25:44.554
dos zaynen geven yidn?

00:25:44.272 --> 00:25:45.009
yidn.

00:25:46.230 --> 00:25:46.860
yo.

00:25:46.888 --> 00:25:50.429
zeyer tokhter lebt un zi iz geven in Shavl

00:25:50.429 --> 00:25:53.345
in der tsayt un zi hot zikh aroysgeratevet,

00:25:53.739 --> 00:25:55.438
un zi lebt in YISRAEL,

00:25:56.270 --> 00:26:00.301
in in Ramat Gan.

00:26:00.301 --> 00:26:00.889
yo.

00:26:01.434 --> 00:26:06.322
iz hobn mir ibergenekhtikt un mir zaynen gegangen vayter.

00:26:06.716 --> 00:26:11.807
zaynen mir gekumen in in Shukyan, dortn iz geven der heym ort fun mayn muter,

00:26:12.285 --> 00:26:15.418
vu ire eltern hobn gehat

00:26:15.525 --> 00:26:18.675
fertsik ⟨hekter⟩ land, zaynen geven ⟨landvirtn⟩.

00:26:18.883 --> 00:26:23.350
un zey flegn makhn di holendishe kez, aza min.

00:26:24.384 --> 00:26:26.724
nu, dortn zaynen mir

00:26:26.882 --> 00:26:31.646
zikh opgeshtelt, di mame's bruder hot nokh gelebt dortn, mit zeyer a groyse familye.

00:26:31.674 --> 00:26:33.997
Yisroel Mikhl.

00:26:34.813 --> 00:26:36.022
Yisroel Mikhl.

00:26:36.956 --> 00:26:43.939
nu, es es hot zikh zeyer geshpirt az es zaynen ongekumen di daytshn.

00:26:43.959 --> 00:26:44.932
me fleg,

00:26:45.579 --> 00:26:50.670
me flegt nit lozn koyfn in mark, me flegt muzn onkumen un gute

00:26:50.760 --> 00:26:53.499
shkheynim zoln aynkoyfn vos tsu esn.

00:26:53.499 --> 00:26:56.272
ir farshteyt? me flegt nit tsulozn keyn yidn.

00:26:56.987 --> 00:26:58.281
nakher

00:26:58.674 --> 00:27:02.679
flegn zey oystrakhtn zikh alerleyke zakhn, undz traybn oyf arbet,

00:27:02.690 --> 00:27:05.024
vashn di diln dortn in

00:27:05.024 --> 00:27:07.240
in in militsye.

00:27:08.411 --> 00:27:12.000
dan hot zikh ongerufn militsye UNK, nakher politsye.

00:27:12.107 --> 00:27:17.063
vashn di diln, vos me hot keyn mol in lebn nit geton, alerleyke shvere arbet UNK.

00:27:17.439 --> 00:27:21.366
un zeyer gut gedenk ikh dem tog,

00:27:21.489 --> 00:27:26.833
shabes iz dos geven, far dem vi me hot undz aroysgetribn fun di shtiber,

00:27:27.210 --> 00:27:28.571
hot men

00:27:29.049 --> 00:27:32.236
gemakht aza k- a kontributsye,

00:27:32.236 --> 00:27:33.223
aroyfgeleygt,

00:27:33.223 --> 00:27:36.755
az me muz tsuzamenkleybn aza un aza sume gelt in gold,

00:27:36.947 --> 00:27:40.975
gedenk ikh hot men tsuzamengeklibn fun di yidn zey hobn altsding tsugenumen.

00:27:41.216 --> 00:27:42.614
un dem rov,

00:27:42.633 --> 00:27:44.905
ot dem Benes- Benesofski,

00:27:45.941 --> 00:27:47.136
hobn zey

00:27:47.173 --> 00:27:50.030
geheysn hakn holts. dos iz geven shabes.

00:27:50.030 --> 00:27:51.217
un trogn

00:27:51.324 --> 00:27:52.449
di holts

00:27:52.640 --> 00:27:54.249
ibern gantsn gas.

00:27:54.249 --> 00:27:57.292
iz er gegangen un geveynt.

00:27:59.795 --> 00:28:01.547
zogt mir dos iz geven in Shukyan?

00:28:01.545 --> 00:28:02.110
yo.

00:28:02.259 --> 00:28:05.021
un der Benesofski iz gekumen in Shukyan oykh?

00:28:04.183 --> 00:28:05.893
yo, oykh un er hot zikh,

00:28:05.893 --> 00:28:07.859
er hot zikh opgeshtelt bay dem

00:28:07.859 --> 00:28:08.972
Shukyaner rov.

00:28:08.992 --> 00:28:11.568
ikh veys afile di shtub, ken ikh aykh vayzn.

00:28:12.215 --> 00:28:16.175
far vos zenen ale kelmer yidn, a sakh kelmer yidn, gegangen oyf Shukyan?

00:28:16.113 --> 00:28:18.886
vayle me hot gezogt az in Shukyan

00:28:18.886 --> 00:28:20.920
iz beserer mentshn, men

00:28:20.920 --> 00:28:23.553
men handlt zikh mit di yidn,

00:28:23.553 --> 00:28:25.510
men bahandlt zikh mit di yidn

00:28:25.510 --> 00:28:27.763
fil mer humanisher,

00:28:27.763 --> 00:28:28.899
vi andersher.

00:28:29.343 --> 00:28:31.718
un in Kelm hot men zikh bahandlt nokh erger, yo?

00:28:31.267 --> 00:28:33.593
nokh erger, in Kelm iz geven nokh erger.

00:28:33.613 --> 00:28:35.112
in Kelm iz geven nokh erger.

00:28:35.115 --> 00:28:36.833
mir hobn gehat,

00:28:36.833 --> 00:28:39.395
mir hobn gehat yedies,

00:28:39.519 --> 00:28:43.516
es iz geven in Kelm nokh eyner a beker, Paglinski, hot er geheysn,

00:28:43.516 --> 00:28:44.644
Paglinski.

00:28:44.767 --> 00:28:47.090
un nakher iz geven eyner a,

00:28:47.349 --> 00:28:48.896
a shofer,

00:28:49.948 --> 00:28:52.660
fun fun daytsh hot er geshtamt,
